    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-threshold factor (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs. required 2) is mitigated by the strong quantitative agreement across all QoIs (E/uval < 0.5 for all metrics) and the use of the production-identical specimen design. Overall credibility sufficient to support regulatory submission for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct.",
